   <div type="translation">
    <head>Translation</head>
    <p>Aurelia Flavia Antonia Elpis, daughter of Neikias, by birth of Italikos (buried) Marcus
     Aurelius Apolloniοs son of Andron (son of Andron son of Andron), <term lang="la">eques</term>,
     chief-doctor, her own husband, in memoriam. </p>
   </div>
